name: jillejr.newtonsoft.json-for-unity
description:
Json.NET is a popular high-performance JSON framework for .NET

This package is a fork of Newtonsoft.Json containing custom builds targeting standalone, portable (UWP, WP8), and AOT targets such as all IL2CPP builds (iOS, WebGL, Android, Windows, Mac OS X, et.al).

Note: This version in particular is a backport of the changes made to Json.NET on to v11.0.2. If you can, you should always use the most up-to-date version. This version exists to support those that have hard dependency on older versions.
